  <brief_title>Effects of Isolated Rooms on the Prevalence of Hospital Acquired Pneumonia in a Respiratory ICU</brief_title>
  <official_title>Epidemiologic Study of Hospital Acquired Pneumonia in a Respiratory ICU</official_title>
